---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy — 8EyeTieDye"
  description="Privacy Policy for 8EyeTieDye — how we collect, use, and protect your data."
>
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20 max-w-3xl">
    <h1
      class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold dye-gradient-text mb-8"
    >
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg space-y-6 text-gray-300">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Effective Date: March 17, 2026</p>

      <p>
        8EyeTieDye ("we," "us," or "our"), a Kinchito Commerce brand, is
        committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how
        we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit
        our website at 8eyetiedye.com (the "Site"). Please read this policy
        carefully. By using the Site, you consent to the practices described in
        this Privacy Policy.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        1. Information We Collect
      </h2>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-3">
        Information You Provide
      </h3>
      <p>We collect information that you voluntarily provide when you:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>
          <strong class="text-white">Place an order:</strong> name, email address,
          shipping address, and phone number (if provided).
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong class="text-white">Contact us:</strong> any information you include
          in your message.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We do not collect or store your payment card information. All payment
        processing is handled securely by Stripe, our third-party payment
        processor.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-6 mb-3">
        Information Collected Automatically
      </h3>
      <p>
        When you visit the Site, we may automatically collect certain
        information, including:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>IP address (used for rate limiting and bot protection)</li>
        <li>Browser type and version</li>
        <li>Pages visited and time spent on the Site</li>
        <li>Referring website or link</li>
        <li>Device type and screen resolution</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        2. Cookies
      </h2>
      <p>We use a single essential cookie to operate the Site:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>
          <strong class="text-white">8etd_session:</strong> A session cookie used
          to track your design generations and maintain your session state. This cookie
          is HMAC-signed for security and expires after 30 days. It does not contain
          personal information.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We do not use advertising cookies, tracking pixels, or third-party
        analytics cookies. We do not participate in cross-site tracking.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        3. How We Use Your Information
      </h2>
      <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Process and fulfill your orders</li>
        <li>Send order confirmation and shipping notification emails</li>
        <li>Respond to your inquiries and provide customer support</li>
        <li>Prevent fraud, abuse, and bot activity</li>
        <li>Enforce our Terms of Service and rate limits</li>
        <li>Improve the Site and our services</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        4. Third-Party Service Providers
      </h2>
      <p>
        We share your information with the following third-party service
        providers, solely for the purposes described below:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>
          <strong class="text-white">Stripe</strong> — Payment processing. Stripe
          receives your payment information directly and is governed by the
          <a
            href="https://stripe.com/privacy"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300 underline"
            >Stripe Privacy Policy</a
          >.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong class="text-white">Printful</strong> — Order fulfillment for apparel
          products. Printful receives your name, shipping address, and order details
          to manufacture and ship your products.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong class="text-white">Cloudflare</strong> — Website hosting, content
          delivery, and security services. Cloudflare processes requests to the Site
          and provides DDoS protection and CDN services.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong class="text-white">Cloudflare Workers AI</strong> — AI image generation
          for tie-dye designs. Design generation runs on Cloudflare's edge infrastructure.
          No personal information is sent to AI models.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third
        parties for their marketing purposes.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        5. Data Retention
      </h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>
          <strong class="text-white">Designs:</strong> AI-generated designs expire
          and are permanently deleted after 24 hours unless purchased. Purchased designs
          are retained as part of your order record.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong class="text-white">Session data:</strong> Session cookies expire
          after 30 days. Session-related data in our key-value store (such as roll
          counts) expires automatically.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong class="text-white">Order data:</strong> We retain order information
          (name, email, shipping address, order details) for as long as necessary
          to fulfill orders, handle disputes, and comply with legal and accounting
          obligations.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong class="text-white">Rate limiting data:</strong> IP-based rate limit
          records are automatically deleted after 24 hours.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        6. Children's Privacy (COPPA)
      </h2>
      <p>
        The Site is not directed to children under the age of 13. We do not
        knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you
        are under 13, you may not use the Site. If we learn that we have
        collected personal information from a child under 13, we will promptly
        delete that information. If you believe a child under 13 has provided us
        with personal information, please contact us at privacy@8eyetiedye.com.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        7. Data Security
      </h2>
      <p>
        We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect
        your information, including:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>HTTPS encryption for all data in transit</li>
        <li>HMAC-signed session cookies to prevent tampering</li>
        <li>Rate limiting to prevent abuse</li>
        <li>No storage of payment card data (handled entirely by Stripe)</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        However, no method of transmission or storage is 100% secure. We cannot
        guarantee absolute security of your information.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        8. Your Rights
      </h2>
      <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your personal information</li>
        <li>Object to or restrict certain processing of your data</li>
        <li>Request a portable copy of your data</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at
        privacy@8eyetiedye.com. We will respond to your request within 30 days.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        9. Changes to This Privacy Policy
      </h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we make
        changes, we will update the "Effective Date" at the top of this page.
        Your continued use of the Site after any changes constitutes your
        acceptance of the revised Privacy Policy. We encourage you to review
        this policy periodically.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        10. Contact Us
      </h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please
        contact us at:
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong class="text-white">8EyeTieDye</strong><br />
        A Kinchito Commerce brand<br />
        Email: privacy@8eyetiedye.com
      </p>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-12">
        8EyeTieDye is a Kinchito Commerce brand. All designs are AI-generated.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
